messages.content: the review system is supposed to be "would you play with this player again?" more than a "performance" rating. if you feel you do not agree with a review, there is also the appeal system using which you can get review/ratings removed, if the appeal is accepted

the reviews and appeals are not moderated.. they are just about how other players "feel".. they are a personal choice.. like i said, if you dont agree with a review, u can appeal it.. if the appeal gets accepted, the review gets removed.. u can also choose to not participate in the runs posted on this server.. everything is a choice
if u hav any suggestions on how to improve the system, those are also welcome at #website-suggestions
or #premium-suggestions as well, since you are a premium member
